result.body: Kaleidoscope by Oriental Weavers is a new machine-woven collection of textured polypropylene. Designs showcase bright, vibrant colors such as sunshine yellow, tangerine, hot pink and bright poppy while ultramarine blue, citron and chartreuse round out the assortment giving the playful colors more drama.
